    <h1>Pre-Roll Ad</h1>
    <p class="description">A video advertisement that plays automatically <strong>before the main video content</strong> on platforms like YouTube, Facebook, and Instagram. Skippable formats charge only for completed views; non-skippable formats guarantee the impression at the cost of viewer goodwill.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
